    <item>
      <title>特朗普在曼哈顿法庭面临财务真相真相时刻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/trump-faces-moment-of-truth-for-his-finances-in-manhattan-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 周一在曼哈顿法庭参加与其一起刑事案件有关的听证会时，他也将面临财务状况的关键时刻：当天的最后期限是要么缴纳保证金以支付 4.54 亿美元的民事诉讼欺诈判决或纽约州启动没收其部分资产的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/trump-faces-moment-of-truth-for-his-finances-in-manhattan-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 14:08:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
